      "updated": 1784212161863,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Mark Russinovich - CTO of Azure (Azure is pretty much keeping Microsoft alive, and it is ALL\nAI all the time) - Ai is a multiplier. It can even multiply negative numbers. \n\n    - In the hands of an inexperienced developer AI is the fastest path from\n        green-field to brown-field development.\n        - green-field - inception, file-new project\n        - brown-field - legacy code that nobody understands and nobody can maintain",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Mark Russinovich - CTO of Azure (Azure is pretty much keeping Microsoft alive, and it is ALL\nAI all the time) - Ai is a multiplier. It can even multiply negative numbers. \n\n    - In the hands of an inexperienced developer AI is the fastest path from\n        green-field to brown-field development.\n        - green-field - inception, file-new project\n        - brown-field - legacy code that nobody understands and nobody can maintain",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
